    "description": "Chamberbound is an atmospheric 3D ball roller puzzle game where you maneuver your way through chambers while solving puzzles with a brilliantly engineered ball which functions in unknown ways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259700/extras/bfc4438e97340b0364a3efc8e53c4536.poster.avif?t=1758126503\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259700/extras/bfc4438e97340b0364a3efc8e53c4536.webm?t=1758126503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259700/extras/bfc4438e97340b0364a3efc8e53c4536.mp4?t=1758126503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br>-Experience a new way of puzzle solving and parkour by taking control of The Ball.<br><br>-Find relations between a set of devices and make use of them to escape.<br><br>-Discover the secrets of the environment you are in as you puzzle your way deeper through chambers.<br><br>-Linear singleplayer with a variety of challenging puzzles.<br><br>-Carefully designed levels and mechanics to create fun and challenging gameplay.<br><br>-Partial controller support.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259700/extras/2fa0efc92e59f10b3fadea976085ec41.poster.avif?t=1758126503\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259700/extras/2fa0efc92e59f10b3fadea976085ec41.webm?t=1758126503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259700/extras/2fa0efc92e59f10b3fadea976085ec41.mp4?t=1758126503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn